00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:59,720
 And it's my favorite character in the Bible besides Jesus,

123
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:02,640
 because his life is so compelling.

124
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:05,240
 He had really high highs, like he

