00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:05,640
 What's the frequency?

192
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:10,160
 All the days of my life.

193
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:16,280
 On the day that David lost his best friend, on all of the four days that each

194
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:21,720
 of his four kids died prematurely, on the day that his daughter was raped,

195
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:26,880
 on the day that one of his sons tried to steal the throne from him,

196
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:31,240
 on the day that he committed murder, on the day that he committed adultery,

197
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:36,200
 on the day that he knocked out a giant, on all of those days,

198
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:45,800
 God's goodness in his mercy was chasing him down, which is amazing.

199
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:50,040
 I mean, do you believe that?

